  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Burundi - Capacity Building Support Project for the Burundian Revenue Office - (PARC-OBR)</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Burundi - Projet d&apos;Appui au Renforcement des Capacit&#xE9;s de l&#x2019;Office Burundais des Recettes - (PARC-OBR)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main beneficiary of the project is the Burundian Revenue Authority.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of the project is to increase the tax and customs revenues of the Republic of Burundi thanks to an improved efficiency of the Burundian Office resulting from a reinforcement of its capacities.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The present concerns the Capacity Building Support Project of the Burundian Revenue Authority (PARC-OBR). It aims at increasing the tax and customs revenues of the Republic of Burundi thanks to an improved efficiency of the Burundian Office resulting from a reinforcement of its capacities. The project is structured around the following components: (i) support for the development of the computer system; (ii) support for skills development in tax and customs matters; and (iii) project management.</narrative>
  </description>
